### 🎥 Browsing Experience
![Aether Nexus Scrolling Experience](file:///C:/Users/user/.gemini/antigravity/brain/79ca68ab-35b7-4589-91bb-3c4af2e23448/aether_nexus_preview_v2_1776818759588.webp)

## ✨ Key Features
- **Responsive Design**: Fully optimized for mobile and desktop.
- **Interactive Elements**: Star background responds to window size; sections reveal smoothly on scroll.
- **Glassmorphism**: Modern UI elements with blur and transparency.
- **Neon Glows**: High-contrast accents for a futuristic vibe.
